message:
Initial Completion

The completion of the main library, docs remaining.

Fixes 2.9.1

Added helper function getAuthCode(), one client for all users, added key concept.
Fixed avatar for users without a profile picture
Made guild, connection, user properties read-only. Updated npm version.
shifted from request to phin to reduce library size
Added linter, configured prettier, added express middleware function
Fixed the main file of the package
Updates for first stable v5 variant
